m8ojmG5-via_lA">Ngọc đài thể kỳ 06 - 玉臺體其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Quy%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-D%C6%B0/author-_4d5nEBX-lxP-MgaFitnXg">Quyền Đức Dư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Qu%C3%BD-H%E1%BB%A3i-l%E1%BA%A1p-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-th%E1%BB%8B-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Chi-T%E1%BB%AD-Lan-nh%E1%BB%8B-thi-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-j8nXYZANpoRMN5lgSF8juA">Quý Hợi lạp nhị thập nhị dạ đề thị Đông Chi, Tử Lan nhị thi hữu - 癸亥腊二十二夜題示東芝子蘭二詩友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-Tr%C3%BAc-chi-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-9/poem-BOpm-aVzVZ1zaIZ57QlBTw">Tây Hồ Trúc chi ca kỳ 9 - 西湖竹枝歌其九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/author-tbuJ74IPkvZZ32WHu1yvJw">Dương Duy Trinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-M%C3%B4n-ch%C3%BAc/poem-5XozGoRP-ImD9G0yFi7Daw">Trường Môn chúc - 長門燭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/author-Xw0ALUMVQ06c4vUGFngNbA">Vương Kiến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Quan-Mi%E1%BA%BFn-Mi%E1%BA%BFn/Y%E1%BA%BFn-T%E1%BB%AD-l%C3%A2u-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-gIMhRigtYlUwyomNjZ28yw">Yến Tử lâu kỳ 1 - 燕子樓其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Quan-Mi%E1%BA%BFn-Mi%E1%BA%BFn/author-N7Xlqjept3_s33DnMuosZw">Quan Miến Miến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
